3rd-party sources included in the e2factory repository and tarball
------------------------------------------------------------------

LDoc and dependencies is used to generate developer documentation:
 - doc/ldoc/LDoc-1.2.0
 - doc/ldoc/Penlight-1.0.2
 - doc/ldoc/luafilesystem-1.6.2

Lua is used for e2factory as well as LDoc:
 - lua/lua-5.1.3

SHA-1 implementation by Steve Reid:
 - generic/sha1.c
